sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Auth Service
    participant C as Category Service
    participant K as Kafka Broker
    participant D as Debt Service
    participant G as Goal Service
    participant T as Transaction Service

    Note over A: Usuario se registra
    A->>K: Produce "user_registered" (topic: auth-events)
    
    Note over C: Usuario crea categoría
    C->>K: Produce "category_created" (topic: category-events)
    
    Note over D: Usuario crea deuda
    D->>K: Produce "debt_created" (topic: debt-events)
    
    Note over G: Usuario crea meta
    G->>K: Produce "goal_created" (topic: goal-events)
    
    Note over T: Usuario crea transacción
    T->>K: Produce "transaction_created" (topic: transaction-events)
    
    Note over K: Los eventos persisten por 7 días
    
    rect rgb(40, 40, 60)
        Note over K: Futuros consumidores (planificados)
        K-->>K: Consumidor de Notificaciones Push
        K-->>K: Consumidor de Análisis de Datos
        K-->>K: Consumidor de Sincronización en Caliente
    end